@0 = ~I never thought I'd come to a place like this, but when the Luskanites burned my home I had nowhere else to go. And that young Tanith who works here sure is handsome...~
@1 = ~I used to look down on everyone who worked here, but maybe I was wrong. Ophala and her girls seem to bring some comfort to the dying soldiers, at least.~
@2 = ~I know you - you saved us from the Wailing Death! You gonna save us all from these Luskan invaders, too?~
